  "detailed_description": "Get ready for a maddening challenge in this parkour game that will push your nerves to the limit. In <strong>\"Park Up Car\"</strong>, you'll face infamous levels designed to be absolutely frustrating.<br><br>Just when you think you're about to achieve success, a tiny mistake will send you sliding back down to the starting point, leaving you on the brink of insanity. The unforgiving mechanics will constantly remind you how easy it is to fail, but only the most tenacious and persevering players will make progress.<br><br>Are you ready to tackle the most frustrating challenge of your life? <strong>\"Park Up Car\"</strong> dares you to conquer the most relentless parkour and showcase your ability to stay calm amidst chaos.<br><br><strong>Warning:</strong> <u>Painfully fun.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538090/extras/4efc20474d28140d60b841e34300657f.poster.avif?t=1710811887\" width=360 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538090/extras/4efc20474d28140d60b841e34300657f.webm?t=1710811887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538090/extras/4efc20474d28140d60b841e34300657f.mp4?t=1710811887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
